These scripts are used to grab the translated MARC21 biblio and authority
field descriptions from the Finnish National Library, and converted into
different formats for use in Koha.

get_fi_xmls.sh will download the xml files.

marc_warnings.pl will report MARC format errors in your database.


Example
-------
    $ ./get_fi_xmls.sh
    $ perl marc_warnings.pl --ignore=9xx > warnings.txt


Requirements
------------
Debian:
  sudo apt-get install libmarc-xml-perl libmarc-record-perl



